      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still bothering with this. the lab results came back and it's just... it's all over. the funding is gone, my advisor won't even look me in the eye, and i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this research. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for a life that doesn't even seem to want me anymore.",
